### 9.3 ERC-8128 HTTP Authentication

Every HTTP request from the robot includes RFC 9421 compliant signatures:

```http
POST /api/telemetry HTTP/1.1
Host: fleet.example.com
Content-Digest: sha-256=:base64hash:
Signature-Input: sig1=("@method" "@path" "content-digest");
    keyid="erc8128:8453:0xRobotWallet";
    created=1708000000;nonce="abc123";
    alg="ecdsa-p256-sha256"
Signature: sig1=:base64_p256_device_signature:
```

For Tier 2 actions, operator cosignature is added:

```http
X-Auth-Cosigner: operator
X-Auth-Cosig: base64_operator_secp256k1_signature
X-Auth-Cosig-Input: ("@method" "@path" "content-digest");
    keyid="operator:0xFleetManager1";
    created=1708000000;nonce="def456"
```

