## 16. Tech Stack Summary

| Layer | Component | Role |
|-------|-----------|------|
| Hardware Identity | ESP32-S3 + ATECC608B | Non-extractable P-256 keypair, device attestation |
| On-Chain Registry | ERC-8004 | Links wallet ↔ device pubkey ↔ endpoints ↔ policy |
| HTTP Authentication | ERC-8128 (RFC 9421) | Per-request cryptographic signing |
| Financial Identity | Privy Server SDK | secp256k1 wallet, on-chain transactions |
| Automated Cosigner | Fleet Policy Server (FastAPI) | Rate limits, geofences, spending caps, attestation |
| Human Authorization | Operator Signer (ESP32-S3 / Mobile) | Stateless signing for Tier 2 escalation |
| Caching | Redis | Policy profiles, nonce tracking, ERC-8004 resolution |

